### Create a new hotel
POST https://localhost:7001/api/hotels
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Grand Hotel & Spa",
  "description": "Luxury 5-star hotel with spa and ocean view",
  "address": "123 Ocean Drive",
  "city": "Miami Beach",
  "state": "FL",
  "country": "USA",
  "postalCode": "33139",
  "phoneNumber": "+1-305-555-0123",
  "email": "info@grandhotel.com",
  "website": "https://grandhotel.com",
  "starRating": 5,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/grand-hotel.jpg",
  "latitude": 25.7617,
  "longitude": -80.1918
}

### Get all hotels
GET https://localhost:7001/api/hotels

### Get hotels by city
GET https://localhost:7001/api/hotels?city=Miami

### Get hotels by minimum star rating
GET https://localhost:7001/api/hotels?minStarRating=4

### Get active hotels only
GET https://localhost:7001/api/hotels?isActive=true

### Get a specific hotel (placeholder - returns 404)
GET https://localhost:7001/api/hotels/{{hotelId}}
